title: Venus targets Singapore berth at HK Open
text: Venus targets Singapore berth at HK Open Saturday, 10 October 2015 (2 minutes ago) HONG KONG (AP) Venus Williams will enter the last-chance saloon at the Hong Kong Open starting Monday as she eyes a berth in the season-ending WTA Finals in Singapore and a top-10 spot for the first time since 2011. Serena Williams Calls Time on 2015 Season After Pulling Out of China Open 00:41 Serena Williams has called time on her 2015 season after withdrawing from the China Open and the WTA Finals in Singapore.
